786
00:45:14,676 --> 00:45:16,326
When we make news these days,

787
00:45:16,436 --> 00:45:19,266
there isn't any chance of success
with just truth as ingredients.

788
00:45:19,356 --> 00:45:21,376
It needs more seasoning.

789
00:45:21,896 --> 00:45:24,256
But you can't take away the taste
of the ingredient, since...

790
00:45:24,346 --> 00:45:25,696
that wouldn't be a news.

791
00:45:26,576 --> 00:45:28,176
It's the age of sympathy these days.

792
00:45:28,596 --> 00:45:31,636
The news also has to bring sympathy
to have a chance of success.

793
00:45:32,156 --> 00:45:36,276
You can make a news that wins
more sympathy from viewers...

794
00:45:36,676 --> 00:45:39,516
if you add the seasoning called
impact to the ingredient...

795
00:45:39,666 --> 00:45:40,876
called truth.

796
00:45:41,006 --> 00:45:42,006
You're kidding me.

